{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/89150", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/89150/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/89150/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/89150/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/89150", "id": 1002634925, "node_id": "I_kwDOAAsO6M47wv6t", "number": 89150, "title": "`TypeId` documentation should mention gotcha re covariant subtypes", "user": {"login": "uazu", "id": 2729716, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjI3Mjk3MTY=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2729716?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/uazu", "html_url": "https://github.com/uazu", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/uazu/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/uazu/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/uazu/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/uazu/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/uazu/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/uazu/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/uazu/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/uazu/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/uazu/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 431251592, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw0MzEyNTE1OTI=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-docs", "name": "A-docs", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: documentation for any part of the project, including the compiler, standard library, and tools"}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2021-09-21T14:46:54Z", "updated_at": "2023-03-30T21:23:22Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "A covariant subtype gets a different type-ID, but can be converted freely from one to the other. This means that taking a type-ID of a generic type argument in a type's `new` method is not guaranteed to give the same type-ID that the type will eventually be called with. The solution is to force the generic type argument to be invariant using PhantomData. See [this bug in `qcell` crate](https://github.com/uazu/qcell/issues/20).\r\n\r\nIt would be helpful if this were documented to avoid similar bugs occurring in other crates.\r\n\r\n```\r\nuse std::any::TypeId;\r\nfn main() {\r\n    println!(\r\n        \"{:?}, {:?}\",\r\n        TypeId::of::<fn(&'_ ())>(),\r\n        TypeId::of::<fn(&'static ())>(),\r\n    );\r\n}\r\n```", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/89150/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/89150/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}